as based insurance holding company has registered a  intrastate public stock offering with the texas securities board trcc was established in  and has successfully raised over  in private placements across texas the shares are available to texas residents through its prospectus trcc is currently owned by over  shareholders the company desires to spread the ownership of trcc throughout texas into every county based on population the companys goal is to complete the offering with over  shareholders texas is one of the largest markets in the country for life insurance with premiums over  billion paid by texas residents in life and annuity premiums each year however over  of the premiums paid by texas residents are paid to companies domiciled outside the state of texas trcc is offering its stock only by means of a public offering prospectus which is available from the company and discusses the companys plan of business and terms of the offering the prospectus also notes specific risks involved in an investment in the companys stock including lack of a liquid public market for shareholders to resell the companys stock and a consequent need to hold the stock for an indefinite period and risks associated with investments in startup insurance companies trccs executive management team and board of directors have over  years of combined insurance and securities experience tim miller trccs president and ceo and gregg zahn trccs chairman have built companies in the past using the same strategy as trcc most recently is first trinity financial corporation ftfc a tulsa oklahoma based insurance holding company which successfully completed private placement and public stock offerings in oklahoma totaling  the board of trcc includes  pat green country music recording artist of fort worth texas  joe mitchell entrepreneur of glen rose texas  steve braley former senior director pga of america of tyler texas  adrian mcdonald insurance professional of bryan texas  j pete laney attorney of austin texas  david cleavinger farmer of wildorado texas  ken davis farmerrancher of grandview texas  eric sandberg texas bankers association of austin texas  randy bailey oil and gas of dallas texas  vernon wolke retired insurance professional of dallas texas   comment on this story share this story contact information timothy millertexas republic capital corporationaustin txusavoice email email us herewebsite visit our website like this story i like it  tweets disclaimer if you have any questions regarding information in this press release please contact the person listed in the contact module of this page please do not attempt to contact  press release newswire we are unable to assist you with any information regarding this release  press release newswire disclaims any content contained in this press release please see our complete terms of service disclaimer for more information